      <p>Same kitchen, same three meals, a dessert, and a daily healing drink — without the herbal drinks. You can always add them later at {usd(products.frozen_herbal_drink_7_1w.price)}/week, or take the standalone Herbal Pack for {usd(products.herbal_drink_pack_30d.price)}.</p>
      <a href={route("/frozen-postpartum-meals/classic", 'en')} class="btn btn-primary">Explore the Frozen Classic Meal</a>
